                        <p>The first step towards change is understanding, and spreading awareness. Justice can only be brought about after clearly identifying injustice.&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>Kendall Jefferys and Autumn Burton are members of the Green Devils Environmental Justice Team.</em></p>

